{
  "stem": "1338.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we did-- we pulled out of the concrete from the back of the plant, and we started growing vegetables.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time, my friends-- you know, and I was somehow put in charge of growing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like we used to guard it and give the vegetables to the ones who really needed it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But who was needing it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was really ridiculous because her mother would come in and say that her daughter is dying of tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We'll give her a carrot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Still going?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so anyway, the wife of the director wanted to be a co-chairman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She needed something to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said, fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a matter, matter, he promised me some milk or some other things, and I said fine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Why not?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was accused by my colleagues that I was cooperating with the capitalists.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I thought that that was most bizarre, and I think this left me with an infallible dislike and complete disdain for any party hacks of any sort because what the hell are they talking about?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What are you going to read Bukharin?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Are you going to read Marx?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you're going to tell me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, what kind of capitalist is this guy?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He died in front of me in Auschwitz, this poor slob.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What kind of a capitalist is he?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Oh, so he had a little bit better food for the time being, who cares?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But in the meantime, I can get something for somebody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Why should I suddenly go into a class war?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There's enough war already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And these kinds of things, I think, influenced me a lot in my behavior later on in terms of joining things, of being part of a group.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
